### Reports defects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/defects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reports orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/orders?dateFrom=2026-03-01&dateTo=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reports tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

